    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Cryptmaster》是一款奇异的地下城探索类冒险游戏，游戏世界中的一切均由言语控制，你可以在其中畅所欲言。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885110/extras/c33dbac468fd16037d1a9bc1617831b2.poster.avif?t=1769536985\" width=780 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885110/extras/c33dbac468fd16037d1a9bc1617831b2.webm?t=1769536985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885110/extras/c33dbac468fd16037d1a9bc1617831b2.mp4?t=1769536985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >很久很久以前，四位勇敢的英雄合力消灭了一个可怕的邪魔，牺牲自我拯救了无数生命。但如今，Cryptmaster惊醒了本该长眠于地下的英雄。为了摆脱这个诡变莫测的死灵法师的束缚，他们必须突破城市下方埋葬地层的重重关卡——阴森的骨屋、神秘的沉海以及怪异的下林。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885110/extras/18c6e16e9c3528cdb482732bc800eea3.poster.avif?t=1769536985\" width=780 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885110/extras/18c6e16e9c3528cdb482732bc800eea3.webm?t=1769536985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885110/extras/18c6e16e9c3528cdb482732bc800eea3.mp4?t=1769536985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手握神秘灵魂石的四位冒险者必须找回他们的记忆，破解古怪的谜题，打败奇异的敌人。在钓鱼、卡牌游戏、吟游诗人饶舌战斗等挑战中，找到正确的词语是成功的关键。谁知道呢，说不定你甚至会想起一点意料之外的东西……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885110/extras/075dc7f320133a2d9bad93e2ea38e0a4.poster.avif?t=1769536985\" width=780 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885110/extras/075dc7f320133a2d9bad93e2ea38e0a4.webm?t=1769536985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885110/extras/075dc7f320133a2d9bad93e2ea38e0a4.mp4?t=1769536985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
